node.text: Take a moment to enjoy the fruits of Mother Earth, not just today but every day. It is our duty to make conscious decisions to ensure the well being of this planet we call home 🌏( & fun fact, my fave place to be is in the water) ( & shout out to my bestie @bria_monique for capturing these dope shots of me on my bday)
